<div class="shop-container">
    <section class="shop-hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">FRESH DISPLAY</span>
        <h1>오늘 먹고 싶은 고기를 한눈에.</h1>
        <p>소, 돼지, 닭을 상황과 요리 목적별로 묶어 고객이 바로 고를 수 있게 구성했습니다.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="shop-scroll-layout">
        <%- include('../../partials/brand-spirit-card', { className: 'market-belief brand-spirit-card' }) %>

        <main class="shop-main-sections">
            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="boss-picks" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607623814075-e51df1bdc82f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="사장추천 / 특가 상품">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge secondary">BEST SELLER</span>
                    <h2>사장추천 / 특가 상품</h2>
                    <p>입고 상태와 판매 반응이 좋은 상품만 앞에 배치했습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% if (sections.bossPicks.length > 0) { %>
                        <% sections.bossPicks.forEach(product => { %>
                            <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="empty-state">추천 메뉴를 준비 중입니다.</div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section bg-alt product-scroll-section" id="theme-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558030006-450675393462?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="어떤 메뉴로 해야지?">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge accent">THEME SHOP</span>
                    <h2>어떤 메뉴로 해야지?</h2>
                    <p>홈파티, 집밥, 야식, 캠핑처럼 구매 상황에 맞춰 보여줍니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="theme-tabs">
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="party">홈파티</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="home_meal">집밥</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="late_night">야식</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="camping">캠핑</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% sections.homeParty.forEach(product => { %>
                        <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="cooking-use-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551028150-64b9f398f678?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="요리 용도용">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge primary">COOKING CUT</span>
                    <h2>요리 용도용</h2>
                    <p>구이, 국·찌개, 볶음·불고기처럼 조리 방식에 맞는 판매 목록입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cooking-tabs">
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="grill">구이용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="soup_stew">국·찌개용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="stir_fry_bulgogi">볶음·불고기용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="braise">찜·조림용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="boil_bossam_jangjorim">수육·보쌈·장조림용</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% sections.cookingUse.forEach(product => { %>
                        <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="family-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604503468506-a8da13d82791?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="가족 식탁 추천">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge primary">CARE SHOP</span>
                    <h2>가족 식탁 추천</h2>
                    <p>아이, 부모님, 1인 가구, 운동 식단까지 목적이 분명한 상품입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="family-tabs">
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="happy_table">가족행복 식탁</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="kids_safe">아이 안심 반찬</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="parents_care">부모님 보양</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="wellness_diet">웰빙/다이어트</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="mixed">혼합용</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid family-product-grid">
                    <% sections.family.forEach(product => { %>
                        <div class="family-product" data-family="<%= product.family_category || 'mixed' %>">
                            <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section camping-ready-section" id="camping-ready" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="캠핑준비 주문하면 끝">
                <div class="section-header camping-section-header">
                    <span class="badge accent">CAMPING SET</span>
                    <h2>캠핑준비 주문하면 끝</h2>
                    <p>사진을 보며 필요한 캠핑 세트를 장바구니에 담고, 마지막에 수령일과 수령지를 확인해 주문합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="camping-ready-copy">
                    <span class="badge accent">CAMPING SET</span>
                    <h2>캠핑준비 주문하면 끝</h2>
                    <p>캠핑용 고기, 야채, 집게와 장갑 같은 고기 먹을 때 필요한 용품을 한 번에 묶어 캠핑장 또는 배송지로 받을 수 있게 접수합니다.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>고기 세트: 구이용 고기와 캠핑 인원에 맞춘 기본 구성</li>
                        <li>야채 세트: 쌈채소, 마늘, 고추, 버섯 등 선택 구성</li>
                        <li>용품 세트: 집게, 위생장갑, 일회용 접시, 숯불 보조용품 메모 가능</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="camping-delivery-note">
                        <strong>수령일 안내</strong>
                        <span>택배는 다음날 도착 기준입니다. 수령희망일이 일요일이거나 연휴 기간이면 캠핑장 대신 배송지에서 받아 가셔야 할 수 있습니다.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="camping-shop-layout">
                    <div class="camping-product-grid">
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="바비큐 고기 세트">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551028150-64b9f398f678?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="바비큐 고기 세트">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">MEAT SET</span>
                                <h3>바비큐 고기 세트</h3>
                                <p>삼겹살, 목살, 소고기 구이용을 인원에 맞춰 구성합니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="쌈채소 야채 세트">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542838132-92c53300491e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="쌈채소 야채 세트">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">VEGETABLE SET</span>
                                <h3>쌈채소 야채 세트</h3>
                                <p>쌈채소, 마늘, 고추, 버섯 등 고기와 같이 먹기 좋은 구성입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="캠핑 식사용품 세트">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523986371872-9d3ba2e2a389?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="캠핑 식사용품 세트">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">CAMPING GOODS</span>
                                <h3>캠핑 식사용품 세트</h3>
                                <p>집게, 위생장갑, 일회용 접시, 간단 소모품을 함께 준비합니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="삼겹살 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1602470520998-f4a52199a3d6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="삼겹살 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">PORK</span>
                                <h3>삼겹살</h3>
                                <p>숯불에 기름이 돌며 고소하게 익는 캠핑 기본 구이용입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="목살 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544025162-d76694265947?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="목살 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">PORK</span>
                                <h3>목살</h3>
                                <p>두툼하게 구워도 담백하고 씹는 맛이 좋은 캠핑용 부위입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="소 토마호크 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558030006-450675393462?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="소 토마호크 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">BEEF TOMAHAWK</span>
                                <h3>토마호크 - 소</h3>
                                <p>캠핑장 메인 요리로 어울리는 묵직한 소고기 구이입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="돼지 토마호크 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529692236671-f1f6cf9683ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="돼지 토마호크 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">PORK TOMAHAWK</span>
                                <h3>토마호크 - 돼지</h3>
                                <p>뼈대가 살아 있어 보기 좋고 굽기 쉬운 돼지고기 캠핑 메뉴입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="안심 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546964124-0cce460f38ef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="안심 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">TENDERLOIN</span>
                                <h3>안심</h3>
                                <p>부드럽게 먹고 싶은 분들을 위한 고급 구이용 단품입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="등심 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551028150-64b9f398f678?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="등심 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">SIRLOIN</span>
                                <h3>등심</h3>
                                <p>풍미와 식감의 균형이 좋아 가족 캠핑 구이에 잘 맞습니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="숯 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508357941501-0924cf312bbd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="숯 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">CHARCOAL</span>
                                <h3>숯</h3>
                                <p>고기와 함께 준비하면 장보기 동선이 줄어드는 캠핑 필수품입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <article class="camping-product-card" data-camping-option="대표 쌈 야채 단품">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542838132-92c53300491e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=85" alt="대표 쌈 야채 단품">
                            <div>
                                <span class="product-kicker">SSAM VEGETABLE</span>
                                <h3>대표 쌈 야채</h3>
                                <p>상추, 깻잎 등 고기와 같이 먹기 좋은 기본 쌈 야채입니다.</p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary camping-cart-button">담기</button>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </div>

                    <div class="camping-cart-panel">
                        <h3>캠핑 장바구니</h3>
                        <p>필요한 세트를 담은 뒤 주문 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
                        <ul id="campingCartList" class="camping-cart-list">
                            <li class="empty">아직 담은 캠핑 세트가 없습니다.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-light" id="campingOrderToggle" disabled>주문 정보 입력</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <form class="camping-order-form" id="campingOrderForm" action="/camping-orders" method="POST" hidden>
                    <input type="hidden" name="package_options" id="campingPackageOptions" value="">
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <label>
                            <span>주문자 이름</span>
                            <input type="text" name="customer_name" autocomplete="name" required>
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>연락처</span>
                            <input type="tel" name="customer_phone" autocomplete="tel" required>
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>이메일</span>
                            <input type="email" name="customer_email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="선택 입력">
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>수령희망일자</span>
                            <input type="date" name="requested_receive_date" id="campingReceiveDate" required>
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>인원</span>
                            <input type="number" name="people_count" min="1" max="30" value="4">
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>세트 수량</span>
                            <input type="number" name="quantity" min="1" max="20" value="1">
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <fieldset class="destination-fieldset">
                        <legend>수령지 선택</legend>
                        <label class="radio-card">
                            <input type="radio" name="destination_type" value="campground" checked>
                            <span>캠핑장에서 받기</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="radio-card">
                            <input type="radio" name="destination_type" value="home">
                            <span>배송지로 받기</span>
                        </label>
                    </fieldset>

                    <div class="campground-fields" id="campgroundFields">
                        <label>
                            <span>캠핑장 이름</span>
                            <input type="text" name="campground_name" id="campgroundName" list="campgroundNames" placeholder="예: 자라섬 캠핑장" required>
                            <datalist id="campgroundNames">
                                <% (campgrounds || []).forEach(campground => { %>
                                    <option value="<%= campground.name %>"><%= campground.address %></option>
                                <% }) %>
                            </datalist>
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <span>캠핑장 주소</span>
                            <input type="text" name="campground_address" id="campgroundAddress" placeholder="새 캠핑장이면 주소를 입력해주세요" required>
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="home-fields" id="homeFields" hidden>
                        <label>
                            <span>배송지 주소</span>
                            <input type="text" name="home_address" id="homeAddress" placeholder="받으실 배송지 주소를 입력해주세요">
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <label>
                        <span>상세주소 / 배송 메모</span>
                        <input type="text" name="delivery_detail" placeholder="관리동 보관, 입구 택배함, 공동현관 등">
                    </label>

                    <label>
                        <span>요청사항</span>
                        <textarea name="customer_memo" rows="3" placeholder="고기 두께, 선호 부위, 추가 용품 요청 등을 적어주세요"></textarea>
                    </label>

                    <div class="camping-warning" id="campingHolidayWarning" hidden>
                        수령희망일이 일요일 또는 연휴 기간이면 캠핑장 배송보다 배송지 수령을 권장합니다. 판매자가 수령희망일자와 수령지를 다시 확인합니다.
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">비회원 캠핑 주문 접수</button>
                </form>
            </section>
        </main>

        <aside class="visual-scroll-nav" aria-label="상품 사진 네비게이션">
            <div class="type-symbol-filter" aria-label="고기 종류 필터">
                <button type="button" data-type="all" title="전체"><span class="type-symbol all" aria-hidden="true">ALL</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="beef" title="소고기">
                    <span class="type-symbol animal animal-cow" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="hanwoo-head" viewBox="0 0 64 64" focusable="false">
                            <path class="hanwoo-ear" d="M18 24 4 17l3 19 14-5M42 25l17-5-7 16-12-5"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-horn" d="M24 18C18 9 17 4 21 2c7 3 9 10 9 17M42 18C49 9 50 4 46 2c-7 3-9 10-9 17"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-face" d="M18 18c7-7 25-7 32 3 5 7 2 24-8 29-9 5-25 0-29-10-3-8-1-16 5-22Z"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-muzzle" d="M12 39c7-5 20-3 24 4 1 7-6 13-17 10-8-2-11-9-7-14Z"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-smile" d="M18 45c6 3 12 2 17-1"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-cheek" d="M46 35c-2 5-5 8-9 10"/>
                            <circle class="hanwoo-eye" cx="39" cy="30" r="2.4"/>
                            <circle class="hanwoo-nose" cx="18" cy="44" r="1.6"/>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </button>
                <button type="button" data-type="pork" title="돼지고기"><span class="type-symbol animal animal-pig" aria-hidden="true">🐷</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="chicken" title="닭고기"><span class="type-symbol animal animal-chicken" aria-hidden="true">🐔</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="etc" title="세트"><span class="type-symbol set" aria-hidden="true">SET</span></button>
            </div>
            <div class="visual-card">
                <img id="floatingVisual" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607623814075-e51df1bdc82f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" alt="사장추천 / 특가 상품">
                <span id="floatingLabel">사장추천 / 특가 상품</span>
            </div>
            <div class="visual-dots">
                <a class="active" href="#boss-picks" data-target="boss-picks">사장추천 / 특가</a>
                <a href="#theme-shop" data-target="theme-shop">상황별 추천</a>
